pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers

Class NewAccController

  • java.lang.Object
    • pt.iade.ManageeMHome.controllers.NewAccController

  • public class NewAccController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a controller to the "new account window" which allows the user to create a new account.

    The "new account window" is in this fxml file: pt.iade.ManageeMHome.views#newAccView.fxml.

    Author:
    jaime
